title: (Weds Part 1) Bobby Tries To Identify 90’s Country Songs in 1 Second! + Major Update on Lunchbox’s Christmas Lights
itunes:title: (Weds Part 1) Bobby Tries To Identify 90’s Country Songs in 1 Second! + Major Update on Lunchbox’s Christmas Lights
description:
Jack White of the White Stripes was recently quizzed on songs by The Beatles and he crushed it! Bobby tries to do the same and identify 90’s country songs just by hearing the first second! Lunchbox shares a major update on the Christmas lights he’s had up all year in spite of his neighbor. He also reveals an interesting dynamic between him and his wife.
